<BaseLayout title="Noah Landesberg" description="Personal site of Noah Landesberg, a product leader working at the intersection of healthcare and AI.">
  <p>
    Bay Area-based product leader working at the intersection of healthcare and
    AI. Most recently at <a href="https://www.getfreed.ai">Freed</a>, and before
    that at <a href="https://www.helloalma.com">Alma</a>,
    <a href="https://www.hioscar.com">Oscar Health</a>, and
    <a href="https://www.athenahealth.com">athenahealth</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    In my spare time I enjoy building software that is mostly useless, including
    an <a href="https://landesbergn.github.io/rhymer/index.html">R package for finding rhyming words</a>,
    an iOS app that tells you what it
    <a href="https://github.com/landesbergn/feels-like">"feels like"</a> outside,
